PN,36701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,FA man who used a "high level of
OL,7,Fviolence" in a confrontation at
OL,8,FManchester Airport - breaking one
OL,9,Ffemale police officer's nose - has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed for three-and-a-half years.
OL,12,FMohammed Fahir Amaaz, 21, struck out
OL,13,Fafter police were called to respond to
OL,14,Fan incident in Terminal 2 on 23 July
OL,15,F2024.
OL,17,FAs he resisted arrest, for an earlier
OL,18,Fassault on a member of the public, he
OL,19,Flanded a number of punches on two
OL,20,Ffemale officers before he was
OL,21,Feventually felled by a Taser.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
