OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,FPC Lydia Ward, who had her nose broken
OL,7,Fby Amaaz, told the court in a victim
OL,8,Fimpact statement she had "never seen
OL,9,Fanyone so violent" and had "never been
OL,10,Fso scared".
OL,12,FPC Ellie Cook, who Amaaz punched her a
OL,13,Fnumber of times, told the court she
OL,14,Fhad been "broken" following the
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
