OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,FAmaaz, from Rochdale, was handed 42
OL,7,Fmonths for assaulting the two officers
OL,8,Fand a member of the public, after a
OL,9,Fjury at Liverpool Crown Court found
OL,10,Fhim guilty following a trial in July
OL,11,F2025.
OL,13,FJailing him, Judge Flewitt criticised
OL,14,Fthe "total lack of remorse" shown by
OL,15,FAmaaz.
OL,17,F"It would have been open to you,
OL,18,Fhaving seen the CCTV, to say there was
OL,19,Fno justification for your attack on
OL,20,FIsmaeil, PC Ward and PC Cook," he said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,F"Instead, you sought to blame others
OL,7,Ffor what was your responsibility and
OL,8,Fportray yourself as the victim. That
OL,9,Fdoes not bode well for your
OL,10,Frehabilitation."
OL,12,FReading a victim impact statement
OL,13,Fduring Amaaz's sentencing, PC Ward
OL,14,Fdescribed herself at the time as a
OL,15,Ffemale who "weighed no more than 8
OL,16,Fstone."
OL,18,FShe said: "You are a male and you
OL,19,Fchose to attack me without a second
OL,20,Fthought.
OL,26,@rD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,F"You chose to attack a female. You
OL,7,Fknocked me to the ground with one
OL,8,Fpunch, with so much force you broke my
OL,9,Fnose.
OL,11,F"How would you feel if a male did that
OL,12,Fto your mother?"
OL,14,FWard continued: "In the moments before
OL,15,Fyou punched me, I remember you looked
OL,16,Fdirectly into my eyes.
OL,18,F"Could you see how scared I was? I was
OL,19,Fpetrified.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,F"I just remember hitting the floor and
OL,7,Fthinking 'this is it'. I felt instant
OL,8,Fpain and then I saw the blood. I
OL,9,Fdidn't know what was going on."
OL,11,FPC Cook's victim impact statement was
OL,12,Fread on her behalf, stating that the
OL,13,Fincident has made her give up her
OL,14,Fdream of being a firearms officer.
OL,16,FThe statement said: "I remember
OL,17,Ffeeling punches in quick succession
OL,18,Fand with such power behind them that I
OL,19,Fthought I was being attacked by 3-4
OL,20,Fpeople. I was terrified.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,F"I quickly thought I'm in a bad place
OL,7,Fand I don't know how to get out of it."
OL,9,FShe added: "I don't think you will
OL,10,Fever begin to understand what you have
OL,11,Fdone to me, or my family. I used to be
OL,12,Fhappy. I used to be driven. I used to
OL,13,Fbe focused. I am now broken."
OL,15,FDuring his trial Amaaz maintained he
OL,16,Fhad been lawfully acting in self
OL,17,Fdefence or in defence of his brother
OL,18,Fwho was also present.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
