PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,FLiverpool Crown Court heard the
OL,7,Fdisturbance began when officers
OL,8,Fapproached Amaaz at a ticket machine
OL,9,Fafter a report a male fitting his
OL,10,Fdescription had earlier headbutted a
OL,11,Fcustomer at Starbucks in arrivals.
OL,13,FThe officers planned to secure the
OL,14,Fsuspect and take him outside, the
OL,15,Fcourt was told.
OL,17,FBut Amaaz began to "tense up and
OL,18,Fresist", with things going from
OL,19,F"nought to a hundred" very quickly.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,FWidely shared mobile phone footage of
OL,7,Fthe incident sparked protests as it
OL,8,Fshowed a young Asian male kicked in
OL,9,Fthe face on the floor by a male police
OL,10,Fofficer who then appeared to stamp
OL,11,Ftowards his head.
OL,13,FCCTV clips leaked days later revealed
OL,14,Fthat beforehand a number of punches
OL,15,Fwere thrown towards the male firearms
OL,16,Fofficer and his two female colleagues.
OL,18,FPC Ward said: "What angers me is that
OL,19,Fafterwards, when only part of the
OL,20,Ffootage was out in the public, you
OL,21,Fplayed the victim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,F"You are not a victim. I am the one
OL,7,Fwho was injured, not you. You had the
OL,8,Fwhole world listening to you and you
OL,9,Fshowed no remorse. Not one ounce."
OL,11,FChief Constable of GMP, Sir Stephen
OL,12,FWatson said his officers had been met
OL,13,Fwith "online vilification,
OL,14,Fcondemnation and adverse commentary"
OL,15,Ffollowing the incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
