OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,F"This incident began after a man was
OL,7,Fheadbutted in a public place in front
OL,8,Fof his family. Our officers were
OL,9,Fresponding quickly to precisely the
OL,10,Fsort of outrageous criminal behaviour
OL,11,Fthat rightly offends the public," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"In undertaking their duties, officers
OL,15,Fwere met with resistance and violence;
OL,16,Ffollowed by online vilification,
OL,17,Fcondemnation and adverse commentary
OL,18,Ffrom those who did not have the full
OL,19,Ffacts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
