OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782647293
OL,3,CMan who used 'high level of violence'
OL,4,Cagainst police officers jailed
OL,6,F"It is vital that officers get the
OL,7,Frespect and support they deserve for
OL,8,Froutinely putting themselves in harm's
OL,9,Fway to protect the public. Assaults on
OL,10,Fpolice officers are sadly all too
OL,11,Fcommon ` 35 of my officers are
OL,12,Fassaulted every week across GM ` and
OL,13,Fsuch incidents can never be justified.
OL,15,FA jury were twice unable to reach a
OL,16,Fverdict on allegations Amaaz and his
OL,17,Fbrother, Muhammad Amaad, 26, assaulted
OL,18,Fanother officer, PC Zachary Marsden.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
